<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>K8s Network Digest — Issue #47</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #050a14;
    --surface: #0b1628;
    --surface2: #0f2040;
    --accent: #00e5ff;
    --accent2: #7c3aed;
    --accent3: #10b981;
    --accent4: #f59e0b;
    --danger: #ef4444;
    --text: #e2e8f0;
    --muted: #64748b;
    --border: #1e3a5f;
    --glow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
    --glow2: 0 0 20px rgba(124,58,237,0.3);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Animated grid background */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(0,229,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,229,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* ─── HEADER ─── */
  header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .header-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .issue-badge {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .date-badge {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 60px 0 50px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    animation: pulse-border 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-border {
    0%, 100% { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
    50% { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.8); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  }

  .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); animation: blink 1s infinite; }
  @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0} }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  h1 span.grad {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .hero-meta span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .hero-meta strong { color: var(--text); }

  /* ─── SECTION TITLES ─── */
  .section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  p { color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 15px; }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM BOXES ─── */
  .diagram-wrap {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .diagram-wrap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2), transparent);
  }

  .diagram-title {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM 1: Pod Network ─── */
  .pod-network {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .node-box {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
  }

  .node-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .pods-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .pod {
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    min-width: 100px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .pod:hover {
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
    box-shadow: var(--glow);
  }

  .pod-ip {
    display: block;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .pod.purple {
    border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.5);
    color: #a78bfa;
    background: rgba(124,58,237,0.06);
  }

  .pod.purple:hover { background: rgba(124,58,237,0.15); box-shadow: var(--glow2); }

  .pod.green {
    border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.5);
    color: #34d399;
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.06);
  }

  .veth-line {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 40px;
    gap: 4px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .veth-line svg { color: var(--accent3); }

  .cbr0 {
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(16,185,129,0.5);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #34d399;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  .cluster-cidr {
    margin-top: 24px;
    background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(245,158,11,0.4);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent4);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .two-nodes {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .arrow-between {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--accent);
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .arrow-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM 2: Service Types ─── */
  .service-diagram {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  .svc-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 20px 16px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    position: relative;
  }

  .svc-card::after {
    content: attr(data-type);
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px; right: -1px;
    font-size: 8px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .svc-card.lb::after { background: var(--accent2); }
  .svc-card.np::after { background: var(--accent4); color: var(--bg); }

  .svc-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .svc-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .flow-box {
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .flow-box.ext { border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.3); color: var(--accent4); background: rgba(245,158,11,0.05); }
  .flow-box.pod-f { border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.3); color: #34d399; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.05); }
  .flow-arrow { text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1; }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM 3: Ingress ─── */
  .ingress-diagram {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .ingress-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .i-box {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 120px;
    background: var(--surface2);
  }

  .i-box.internet { border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.5); color: var(--accent4); background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08); }
  .i-box.ctrl { border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.5); color: #a78bfa; background: rgba(124,58,237,0.08); }
  .i-box.svc1 { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.4); color: var(--accent); }
  .i-box.svc2 { border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.4); color: #34d399; }

  .i-arrow { font-size: 20px; color: var(--muted); padding: 0 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .ingress-rules {
    margin-top: 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .rule-item {
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .rule-host { color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .rule-path { color: var(--muted); }
  .rule-arrow { color: #34d399; }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM 4: CNI ─── */
  .cni-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  .cni-plugin {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 20px 12px;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--surface2);
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .cni-plugin:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.05);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cni-icon { font-size: 28px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .cni-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .cni-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 9px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .cni-tag.p { background: rgba(124,58,237,0.1); border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.3); color: #a78bfa; }
  .cni-tag.g { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1); border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.3); color: #34d399; }
  .cni-tag.y { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.3); color: var(--accent4); }

  .cni-desc { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM 5: NetworkPolicy ─── */
  .netpol-diagram {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .ns-box {
    border: 1px dashed var(--border);
    padding: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ns-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 12px;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 0 8px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .ns-box.allowed { border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.5); }
  .ns-box.blocked { border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.4); }

  .policy-center {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  .policy-icon {
    background: rgba(124,58,237,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.5);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #a78bfa;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100px;
  }

  .allow-line { color: #34d399; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .block-line { color: var(--danger); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-decoration: line-through; }

  .traffic-pod {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .traffic-pod.ok { border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.5); color: #34d399; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.05); }
  .traffic-pod.bad { border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.4); color: var(--danger); background: rgba(239,68,68,0.05); }

  /* ─── DIAGRAM 6: DNS ─── */
  .dns-flow {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .dns-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .dns-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dns-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .dns-query { color: var(--accent4); display: block; }
  .dns-result { color: #34d399; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 4px; display: block; }

  .dns-arch {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .dns-comp {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .dns-comp-name { color: var(--accent2); display: block; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; }
  .dns-comp-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ─── ARTICLE CARD ─── */
  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .article-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--surface);
    transition: all 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.03);
  }

  .article-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3px; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), transparent);
  }

  .card-cat {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .card-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
  .card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ─── TIPS SECTION ─── */
  .tips-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .tip-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 20px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tip-number {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(0,229,255,0.1);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  }

  .tip-title { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tip-code {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent3);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #34d399;
    line-height: 1.7;
    white-space: pre;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    padding: 40px 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .footer-brand { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .two-nodes, .service-diagram, .cni-grid, .netpol-diagram,
    .dns-arch, .article-grid, .tips-grid, .ingress-rules { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ingress-flow { flex-direction: column; }
    .i-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  }

  /* ─── ANIMATE IN ─── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .section { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both; }
  .section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }

  .tag-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .tag {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .highlight-box {
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="header-top">
      <div class="issue-badge"><span class="dot"></span> &nbsp; K8S NETWORK DIGEST</div>
      <div class="date-badge">MARCH 05, 2026 · ISSUE #47</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-tag"><span class="dot"></span> WEEKLY DEEP DIVE BY VISHAL ABHINAV</div>
      <h1>Kubernetes<br><span class="grad">Networking</span><br>Decoded</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Everything you need to understand Pod networks, Services, Ingress, CNI plugins, NetworkPolicy, and CoreDNS — with visual diagrams.</p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span>📡 <strong>6</strong> Diagrams</span>
        <span>📚 <strong>8</strong> Articles</span>
        <span>⚡ <strong>3</strong> Pro Tips</span>
        <span>⏱ <strong>12 min</strong> read</span>
		<span>⏱ <strong>Er.Vishal Abhinav</strong> Author</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- SECTION 1: POD NETWORKING -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">// DIAGRAM 01</div>
    <h2>Pod-to-Pod Networking</h2>
    <p>In Kubernetes, every Pod gets its own unique IP address. Pods communicate directly without NAT — whether on the same node or across nodes — via the cluster's overlay or underlay network.</p>

    <div class="diagram-wrap">
      <div class="diagram-title">FIG 1.0 — KUBERNETES POD NETWORK MODEL (MULTI-NODE)</div>

      <div class="two-nodes">
        <!-- Node 1 -->
        <div class="node-box">
          <div class="node-label">◈ NODE 1 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 192.168.1.10</div>
          <div class="pods-row">
